     C                     ENDSR
**  ER
E-01 INPUT PARTS NO
E-02 INPUT BEGINNING DATE
E-03 INPUT YEAR
E-04 INPUT MONTH
E-05 INPUT DAY
E-06 NO DATA
E-07 I INDICATE THE LAST DATA
E-08 I INDICATE THE FIRST DATA
E-09 I CAN'T SELECT MORE THAN 2
E-10 MONTH ISN'T RIGHT
E-11 DAY ISN'T RIGHT
